=>How to Run the Project

#Step 1: Install JSON Server (If not installed)

npm install -g json-server

#Step 2: Navigate to Project Folder

cd event-management

#Step 3: Run JSON Server

json-server --watch db.json --port 3000

#Step 4: Open Project

Use Live Server in VS Code and open:


index.html


=>API Endpoints Used

* GET /events
* POST /events
* PUT /events/:id
* DELETE /events/:id
* GET /registrations
* POST /registrations

Base URL:

http://localhost:3000


